## ✨ Features

### Sections Included
1. **Header Navigation** - Sticky header with mobile menu
2. **Hero Section** - Video background with animations
3. **Why Choose Us** - 6 key features
4. **Portfolio** - Grid gallery with filtering & lightbox
5. **European Modern Classic Collection** - 8 curated house types with investment projections
6. **Services** - Design, Build, Interior, Furniture
7. **Integrated Benefits** - Comparison section
8. **Testimonials** - Client reviews with ratings
9. **Free Survey CTA** - Lead generation section
10. **Coverage Area** - Service locations
11. **Footer** - Contact & links

### Technology Stack
- **React 18** - UI library
- **TypeScript** - Type safety
- **Vite** - Lightning-fast build tool
- **Framer Motion** - Smooth animations
- **Lucide React** - Icon library
- **TailwindCSS compatible** - Utility styling

