## 🚀 Deployment

### Deploy to Vercel (Recommended)

1. **Push to GitHub:**
```bash
git init
git add .
git commit -m "ADITYARCH Premium Website - Ready to Deploy"
git remote add origin https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/adityarch-website.git
git branch -M main
git push -u origin main
```

2. **Deploy to Vercel:**
   - Go to vercel.com
   - Sign up with GitHub
   - Click "Import Project"
   - Paste GitHub URL
   - Click "Deploy"
   - Wait 3-5 minutes
   - Get live URL!

### Deploy to Netlify

1. Connect GitHub repository
2. Build command: `npm run build`
3. Publish directory: `dist`
4. Deploy!

### Deploy to Firebase Hosting

```bash
npm install -g firebase-tools
firebase login
firebase init hosting
npm run build
firebase deploy
```

